{"blogid": "120005652", "writerAge": "码龄3年", "writerBlogNum": "9", "writerCollect": "56", "writerComment": "9", "writerFan": "12", "writerGrade": "2级", "writerIntegral": "132", "writerName": "_CBW_", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_120005652.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "342936", "writerRankWeekly": "183706", "writerThumb": "23", "writerVisitNum": "16293", "blog_read_count": "9065", "blog_time": "于 2021-08-30 21:50:52 发布", "blog_title": "VS+Opencv出现：xxx处有未经处理的异常: Microsoft C++ 异常: cv::Exception，位于内存位置xxx处。", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"1__0\"></a>1. 问题描述</h1>\n<p>opencv配置运行时报错<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\fba92a18ea7e40ad824134afb293b30c.png\"/><br/> 代码如下：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span>  </span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;opencv2/core/core.hpp&gt;</span>  </span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;opencv2/highgui/highgui.hpp&gt;</span>  </span>\n\nusing namespace cv<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{<!-- --></span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 读入一张图片    </span>\n\tMat img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">imread</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"‪D:\\\\opencvTest.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 创建一个名为 \"图片\"窗口    </span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">namedWindow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"图片\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 在窗口中显示图片   </span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">imshow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"图片\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">// 等待6000 ms后窗口自动关闭    </span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">waitKey</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">6000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>错误提示：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>0x00007FFBDC754ED9 处(位于 test.exe 中)有未经处理的异常: Microsoft C++ 异常: cv::Exception，位于内存位置 0x000000229E91F3B0 处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1><a id=\"2_29\"></a>2.解决方法</h1>\n<p>1.路径出错：这里的imread函数的路径为<strong>双反斜杠</strong>、<strong>不必非要放在解决方案路径下（一家之言，我这里不用）</strong><br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\d4fa4eec202e4e43ab9de67ef09b302f.png\"/><br/> 尤其是要注意：<strong>这里的路径是不能粘贴属性-&gt;安全-&gt;对象名称</strong>，会附带符号<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\bc4abe83773b4b36b34df404c6430b54.png\"/><br/> 重新<strong>手动录入路径</strong>或在<strong>文件夹目录处复制路径（如下图）</strong> 可以正常使用</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ebb2db6929aa4f8792ef8de7f56f9755.png\"/></p>\n<h1><a id=\"2__38\"></a>2. 属性出错</h1>\n<p>opencv_world410d.lib和opencv_world410.lib分开放在不同的.prop中，其中<br/> opencv_world410d.lib为Debug版，不要加上opencv_world410.lib；<br/> opencv_world410.lib为Release版，不要加上opencv_world410d.lib；<br/> 上述为：属性-&gt;链接器-&gt;输入-&gt;添加依赖项中，输入和继承的部分，若两个都有，则建议删除不是对应的<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\a1de14e7e7344df9abd9d1a839e0f07b.png\"/></p>\n<h1><a id=\"3__44\"></a>3 .其他错误（个人）</h1>\n<ol><li>程序出错：设置断点自行调节，检查函数是否使用规范，检查图片路径是否正确（双反斜杠，绝对路径）</li><li>图片出错：图片过大或图片有问题</li><li>Mat出错卡死：虽然上述描述的问题，应该不会是这个出错导致的，但很常见，在mat的注释和代码之间多敲几个回车，或删掉mat注释（光标双击选中mat，按F12）</li></ol>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "C++", "cpp": 1, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2021-08-30 21:50:52", "summary": "问题描述配置运行时报错在这里插入图片描述代码如下：读入一张图片创建一个名为图片窗口图片在窗口中显示图片图片等待后窗口自动关闭错误提示：处位于中有未经处理的异常异常，位于内存位置处。解决方法路径出错：这"}